abic text-gold text-xs leading-tight\">المعاقبة</p><p class=\"text-text-primary font-medium text-xs mt-0.5\">Mu&#x27;aqaba</p><p class=\"text-text-muted text-[10px] mt-0.5\">Course correct</p></div><div class=\"glass-card py-3 px-2 text-center cursor-default\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px) scale(0.96)\"><p class=\"arabic text-gold text-xs leading-tight\">المجاهدة</p><p class=\"text-text-primary font-medium text-xs mt-0.5\">Mujahada</p><p class=\"text-text-muted text-[10px] mt-0.5\">Strive</p></div><div class=\"glass-card py-3 px-2 text-center cursor-default\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px) scale(0.96)\"><p class=\"arabic text-gold text-xs leading-tight\">المعاتبة</p><p class=\"text-text-primary font-medium text-xs mt-0.5\">Mu&#x27;ataba</p><p class=\"text-text-muted text-[10px] mt-0.5\">Gentle review</p></div></div><div class=\"mb-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><button class=\"btn-gold flex items-center gap-3 text-base\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92a5.06 5.06 0 01-2.2 3.32v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.1z\" fill=\"#0a0a0f\"></path><path d=\"M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z\" fill=\"#0a0a0f\"></path><path d=\"M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l2.85-2.22.81-.62z\" fill=\"#0a0a0f\"></path><path d=\"M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z\" fill=\"#0a0a0f\"></path></svg>Continue with Google</button></div><p class=\"text-text-muted text-xs tracking-wide\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">Begin with Bismillah. End with Shukr.</p></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-697813154b7cbb1f.js\" id=